- 1969: **Regan** was stockbroker looking to do something better
- Hedging seemed good way to start partnership
- Made list of 4 potential partners; Thorp on it
- Search began after **Beat the Market** published (received fair publicity)
- Good fit: Regan handled business/administrative side, Thorp did what Regan couldn't do

